sectionText: Restricted to Students in the History Honors Program.   Meets with HIST 498, Section:  B. Topic:  Empires:  Mongols, Ottomans, Habsburgs. Description:  An inquiry into the nature of empires and their place in history.  The Mongol, Ottoman, and Habsburg empires will serve as case studies.
